  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>Describe the process of nuclear fusion in terms of its product and reactants</item>
<item>Calculate the energies of particles produced by a fusion reaction</item>
<item>Explain the fission concept in the context of fusion bombs, the production of energy by the Sun, and nucleosynthesis</item>
</list></md:abstract>
